 match ip dscp af31 
class-map match-any VOIP_RTP
 match ip dscp ef 
 match ip precedence 5

  bandwidth remaining percent 1 
 class VOIP_RTP
  priority

 action 3.0 regexp "RUNNING" "$_cli_result" line
 action 4.0 if $_regexp_result eq "0"

 action 5.0  cli command "guestshell enable"
